# my-app2 website

## Framework

- Next.js App Router (`app/`), React 19, TypeScript.
- This repo’s Next.js differs from generic training data. Before changing routing, config, or Next APIs, read the matching topic under `node_modules/next/dist/docs/` and respect deprecations (see `AGENTS.md`).

## Styling and components

- Tailwind CSS v4; use utility classes consistently.
- Prefer existing primitives: `class-variance-authority`, `clsx`, `tailwind-merge`, Radix/shadcn patterns already in the project when adding UI.
- Visual language: light backgrounds `bg-zinc-50` / `bg-white`, dark mode `dark:bg-black` with `text-zinc-*` for body and `text-black` / `dark:text-zinc-50` for emphasis. Keep `font-sans` unless a page intentionally changes typography.

## Images and links

- Use `next/image` for static images under `public/`. Set `width`/`height` (or fill + layout) and meaningful `alt`.
- External links: `target="_blank"` with `rel="noopener noreferrer"`.

## Scope

- Prefer small, focused changes; match patterns in neighboring files when extending the app.
